
A set of instructions turned into a word


def function (arg1, arg2)       # arguemnet = arg
    ans = arg1 + arg2           Variables inside the function exist only in the function
    print(ans)
return

x = function(3,5)       #   3 = arg1    4 = arg2
print(x)                #   output = 8
print(ans)              #   output error



When calling functions enter the arguements based on index value.